    <briefdescription>
<para>RAII pair: owns a <ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_client_1_1_managed_server" kindref="compound">Client::ManagedServer</ref> child process and a connected <ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_tryll_client" kindref="compound">TryllClient</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Move-only. On destruction, the <ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_tryll_client" kindref="compound">TryllClient</ref> is shut down first (graceful TCP close), then the <ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_client_1_1_managed_server" kindref="compound">Client::ManagedServer</ref> is stopped (process termination). The declaration order of the members enforces this.</para>
<para>Obtain a <ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_connected_session" kindref="compound">ConnectedSession</ref> via <ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_tryll_client_1aa56dfab6c46abdc5be450e8f0ed91114" kindref="member">TryllClient::RunAndConnect</ref>.</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>session<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_tryll_client_1aa56dfab6c46abdc5be450e8f0ed91114" kindref="member">Tryll::TryllClient::RunAndConnect</ref>(opts);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">session.GetClient().ConfigureSession(Tryll::Client::InferenceEngine::LlamaCpp);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>…</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
